---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Why LRA Cloud Operations"
  descripcion="The case for specialized DevOps over generalist consultancies. Direct access to senior engineers, faster time-to-production, and full ownership from day one."
  keywords="DevOps consulting Spain, specialized cloud engineers, platform engineering team, AWS consultancy"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-28 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);">
        Why us
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Why LRA Cloud Operations?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
        The case for specialized over generalist
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUE PROPS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-8">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">Direct access to senior engineers</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
          When you work with LRA, you work directly with the engineers building your infrastructure — not an account manager or a project coordinator. Every decision is made by someone who will also implement it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">Speed that large consultancies can't match</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
          Enterprise consultancies spend months on SOW negotiation, staffing and onboarding. We start within 2 weeks. Our first delivery milestone is typically week 3.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">You own everything from day one</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
          No proprietary tooling. No lock-in. Everything we build uses open standards — Terraform, Kubernetes, GitHub Actions. If you decide to bring it in-house, the transition is seamless.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">Accountability without layers</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
          In large consultancies, accountability is distributed across 10 people. With us, you have one point of contact who owns the outcome — and whose reputation depends on it.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section class="py-16 border-t border-gray-100" style="background: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">LRA vs. the alternatives</h2>
        <p class="text-sm mt-2" style="color: #64748b;">A direct comparison across the dimensions that matter most</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(10,37,64,0.06);">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #94a3b8; background: #f8fafc;"></th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #1E6FFF; background: #EEF4FF;">LRA Cloud Ops</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #64748b; background: #f8fafc;">DevOps FTE (Spain)</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #64748b; background: #f8fafc;">Big Consultancy</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {[
                { label: 'Cost', lra: '€8K–25K/project', fte: '€45K–70K/year + benefits', big: '€150K–400K/project' },
                { label: 'Start time', lra: '1–2 weeks', fte: '2–4 months hiring', big: '3–6 months' },
                { label: 'Senior access', lra: 'Direct', fte: 'Depends on hire', big: 'Via account manager' },
                { label: 'Accountability', lra: 'Full ownership', fte: 'Internal politics', big: 'Diluted' },
                { label: 'Flexibility', lra: 'Scope-based', fte: 'Fixed headcount', big: 'Contract lock-in' },
              ].map(({ label, lra, fte, big }, i) => (
                <tr style={i % 2 === 0 ? 'background: white;' : 'background: #fafbfc;'}>
                  <td class="px-6 py-3.5 text-xs font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">{label}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-3.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #1E6FFF; background: rgba(238,244,255,0.5);">{lra}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-3.5 text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">{fte}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-3.5 text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">{big}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5" style="color: #0A2540;">Ready to see how we work?</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]"
          style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.35);">
          See how we work
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold px-7 py-4 rounded-xl border transition-all hover:bg-gray-50"
          style="color: #0A2540; border-color: #e2e8f0;">
          View engagement models
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
